text: Prem Nagar is a village in the Bhiwani district of the Indian state of Haryana. It lies approximately north of the district headquarters town of Bhiwani. , the village had 684 households with a total population of 3,495 of which 1,849 were male and 1,646 female. ==References== Category:Villages in Bhiwani district
title: Prem Nagar, Bhiwani
